fields.title: Peaky Blinders
fields.review: Raw, dramatic and surprisingly realistic for a series set in the 1920s. The acting is superb and the storylines are gripping.

fields.title: Red Notice
fields.review: A great action film with a great cast. The story is a little far fetched but it's a fun watch.
